@startuml A2_01_component_agent_service_simple
title Agent Service – Simplified View

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #000000
  BorderThickness 1
}

rectangle "Agent Service\nPort: 8000" as AGENT_SERVICE {
  rectangle "API Layer\n(auth, chat, documents)" as API_LAYER
  rectangle "LangGraph Agent\n+ Tool System" as CORE
  rectangle "Session & Memory\nManagement" as STATE
}

database "Postgres" as DB
cloud "RAG Service" as RAG
cloud "Enrollment Service" as ENROLLMENT
cloud "OpenAI" as OPENAI
cloud "Observability" as OBS

API_LAYER --> CORE
CORE --> STATE
CORE --> RAG : enrollment tools
CORE --> ENROLLMENT : enrollment tools
CORE --> OPENAI : LLM
STATE --> DB : sessions, checkpoints
AGENT_SERVICE --> OBS

note right of AGENT_SERVICE
**Role:** Stateful Orchestrator
**Tech:** FastAPI + LangGraph
**Key Functions:**
- User interaction & chat
- Tool coordination
- Session management
- Conversation state
end note

@enduml

